OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1774455107
OL,3,CWoman whose ex tried to murder her by
OL,4,Ccrashing into funeral parlour wins
OL,5,Cpayout
OL,7,FA woman whose former partner tried to
OL,8,Fmurder her and her mother by driving a
OL,9,Fcar into the Jedburgh funeral home
OL,10,Fwhere she worked has won a
OL,11,Fcompensation payout.
OL,13,FFormer police officer William McBurnie
OL,14,Fwas jailed for 11 years after he
OL,15,Fadmitted attempting to murder Zoe
OL,16,FTurnbull and her mother Beverly.
OL,18,FHe admitted driving the car at them
OL,19,F"at speed" through the window of Zoe
OL,20,FTurnbull Funeral Directors in Market
OL,21,FPlace, Jedburgh, on December 7, 2022.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1774455107
OL,3,CWoman whose ex tried to murder her by
OL,4,Ccrashing into funeral parlour wins
OL,5,Cpayout
OL,7,FDigby Brown Solicitors, acting for Ms
OL,8,FTurnbull, confirmed the civil action
OL,9,Fshe brought against McBurnie has now
OL,10,Fconcluded and the case has been
OL,11,Fsettled for an undisclosed amount.
OL,13,FMcBurnie was handed a 13-year extended
OL,14,Fsentence comprising 11 years in
OL,15,Fcustody and two years of supervision
OL,16,Fon his release from prison when he was
OL,17,Fsentenced at the High Court in
OL,18,FLivingston in October 2024.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1774455107
OL,3,CWoman whose ex tried to murder her by
OL,4,Ccrashing into funeral parlour wins
OL,5,Cpayout
OL,7,FSentencing McBurnie, then 57, Lord
OL,8,FMulholland said he turned his vehicle
OL,9,Finto a "lethal weapon and used it with
OL,10,Fdevastating effect".
OL,12,FIn a statement issued after the
OL,13,Fsentencing, Ms Turnbull described
OL,14,FMcBurnie as the "Jekyll and Hyde of
OL,15,FJedburgh ` charming in public but
OL,16,Fdangerous behind the scenes".
OL,18,FShe said he was a "forceful monster
OL,19,Fwho encroached on our lives and used
OL,20,Fviolence to get his own way".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1774455107
OL,3,CWoman whose ex tried to murder her by
OL,4,Ccrashing into funeral parlour wins
OL,5,Cpayout
OL,7,FShe also urged anyone in a similar
OL,8,Fsituation not to wait for the worst to
OL,9,Fhappen before acting.
OL,11,FMs Turnbull said: "You have a voice
OL,12,Fand there are so many people around
OL,13,Fyou ready to listen ` and act ` so you
OL,14,Fcan get the help you need."
OL,16,FThe car narrowly missed the women but
OL,17,Fthey were both injured in the
OL,18,Fincident, with one hit by debris.
OL,20,FMcBurnie previously served with the
OL,21,FPolice Service of Northern Ireland.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1774455107
OL,3,CWoman whose ex tried to murder her by
OL,4,Ccrashing into funeral parlour wins
OL,5,Cpayout
OL,7,FAt the sentencing hearing Gareth Jones
OL,8,FKC, representing McBurnie, said the
OL,9,Fformer police officer felt
OL,10,F"significant remorse" for his actions
OL,11,Fand was "appalled" by his behaviour.
OL,13,FMairi Day, partner at Digby Brown
OL,14,FSolicitors, said: "What happened to
OL,15,FZoe and her mother was life-changing `
OL,16,Fthey suffered physical and emotional
OL,17,Fharm that will likely impact them both
OL,18,Fforever.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1774455107
OL,3,CWoman whose ex tried to murder her by
OL,4,Ccrashing into funeral parlour wins
OL,5,Cpayout
OL,7,F"After everything Zoe has gone through
OL,8,Fshe has understandably requested
OL,9,Fprivacy so I will not discuss the
OL,10,Fparticulars of her civil action other
OL,11,Fthan to confirm the case has now
OL,12,Fsettled.
OL,14,F"I hope the end of the criminal and
OL,15,Fcivil proceedings means Zoe can
OL,16,Ffinally close this distressing chapter
OL,17,Fand focus on a positive future."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
